OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784796494
OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Miliband told
OL,8,Fministers from ASEAN (Association of
OL,9,FSoutheast Asian Nations) member
OL,10,Fstates: "I know in particular how much
OL,11,Fthe Iran conflict is affecting Asean
OL,12,Fpartners.
OL,14,F"You are feeling as much as anyone
OL,15,Facross the world the daily impact on
OL,16,Fyour economies and the living
OL,17,Fstandards of your citizens, as well
OL,18,Findeed as the impact on seafarers from
OL,19,Fmany Asean nations.
OL,26,@rD@IOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784796494
OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,F"We too in the UK, in our own way, are
OL,8,Ffeeling the effects of the conflict on
OL,9,Ffamilies and businesses in the impacts
OL,10,Fon the cost of living."
OL,12,FThe foreign secretary added that the
OL,13,FUK "will work intensively with others
OL,14,Fto seek to de-escalate this conflict
OL,15,Fand find a diplomatic way forward".
OL,17,FAny solution "must include reopening
OL,18,Fthe Strait of Hormuz and upholding the
OL,19,Ffundamental principle of freedom of
OL,20,Fnavigation", he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@WO]uD@DOUwD@bO]yD@NOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
