OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FMiliband also said he welcomed a
OL,8,Fmemorandum of understanding signed in
OL,9,FJune between the US and Iran, which
OL,10,Fincludes a deal for toll-free passage
OL,11,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz for 60
OL,12,Fdays.
OL,14,FBut efforts to hold onto the deal
OL,15,Fstalled after Iran targeted tankers in
OL,16,Fthe Strait of Hormuz earlier this
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,19,FAt the time, Trump took to Truth
OL,20,FSocial to declare that "the Cease Fire
OL,21,Fis OVER!"
OL,26,@|D@XOU}D@IO]
