OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FTrump took to the platform again on
OL,8,FWednesday, when he wrote: "From this
OL,9,Fpoint forward, any time the Islamic
OL,10,FRepublic of Iran shoots at a ship in
OL,11,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, whether it be by
OL,12,FMissile, Rocket, Drone, or any other
OL,13,Fdevice or weapon, the United States
OL,14,Fwill bomb and destroy ONE BRIDGE OR
OL,15,FPOWER PLANT, including those located
OL,16,Fnext to, or in, the Capital City of
OL,17,FTehran."
OL,26,@pD@[OUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
