OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThe warning came after the US carried
OL,8,Fout another wave of strikes on Iran,
OL,9,Fwhere air defences opened fire over
OL,10,FTehran.
OL,12,FIran launched a missile attack on
OL,13,FAqaba, Jordan, and alerts were issued
OL,14,Fin Bahrain and Saudi Arabia.
OL,16,FJordan's military said it intercepted
OL,17,Ffour Iranian missiles over Aqaba,
OL,18,Fwhile two others fell in "uninhabited
OL,19,Fareas".
OL,21,FSaudi Arabia nuclear deal
OL,26,@zD@ZOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
