OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FOn Wednesday the Trump administration
OL,8,Fapproved an agreement with Saudi
OL,9,FArabia, reportedly allowing the
OL,10,Fkingdom nation to develop a civilian
OL,11,Fnuclear energy programme.
OL,13,FWashington released scant details of
OL,14,Fthe deal, but the framework paves the
OL,15,Fway for the building of a uranium
OL,16,Fenrichment facility in Saudi Arabia
OL,17,Fafter a joint US-Saudi study,
OL,18,Faccording to sources close to the deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784796494
OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,F"These agreements reflect our two
OL,8,Fnations' shared commitment to
OL,9,Fstrengthening US-Saudi commercial
OL,10,Frelations, delivering prosperity at
OL,11,Fhome and security to our allies
OL,12,Fabroad," US Energy Secretary Chris
OL,13,FWright said in a statement.
OL,15,F"Rest assured, these agreements uphold
OL,16,Fthe highest standards of nuclear
OL,17,Fsafety and nonproliferation, while
OL,18,Frelying on the world's best nuclear
OL,19,Ftechnology and scientists, designed
OL,20,Fright here in the United States."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@HO]wD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784796494
OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FIn a statement the US Department of
OL,8,FEnergy said the agreement "provides
OL,9,Fgreat access for American companies in
OL,10,Fthe Saudi nuclear energy program,
OL,11,Fbenefiting American industry, workers,
OL,12,Fand supply chains while helping to
OL,13,Fmeet Saudi energy needs".
OL,26,@pD@[OUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
