OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThe agreement does not include the
OL,8,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency 's
OL,9,FAdditional Protocol, which would allow
OL,10,Ffor more monitoring, inspections and
OL,11,Fverification, according to one of the
OL,12,Fpeople familiar with the decision.
OL,14,FThe deal is expected to last 30 years
OL,15,Fand involve U.S. firms in developing
OL,16,Fthe program. The Energy Department in
OL,17,Fa statement said it will be submitted
OL,18,Ffor review to Congress, where it could
OL,19,Fface opposition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
