OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FRubio blamed Iran for the Houthi
OL,8,Frebels' naval blockade against Saudi
OL,9,FArabia but said he hoped the situation
OL,10,Fcould be de-escalated.
OL,12,FThe Houthis are armed and
OL,13,Fsignificantly influenced by Iran but
OL,14,Foperate independently of Iran's
OL,15,Fsupreme leader, unlike the Lebanese
OL,16,Fmilitant group Hezbollah and several
OL,17,FIran-backed Iraqi militias.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
