OL,3,CMiliband urges calm as Trump threatens
OL,4,Cto bomb Iranian bridges and power
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,F"Anything that restricts shipping
OL,8,Fthrough the Red Sea would be
OL,9,Fproblematic for the same reasons that
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz is problematic,"
OL,11,FRubio said on the sidelines of a
OL,12,Fregional summit in the Philippines.
OL,14,FThe US is closely monitoring the
OL,15,Fsituation, he said, and has contacted
OL,16,FSaudi Arabia a number of times over
OL,17,Fthe last week about the threats.
